7T09:17:07.000Z","msg":"波圖無喎"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:17:34.000Z","msg":"國米都好似無"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"佢搞得掂國米班大佬 辛隊同馬達拉斯都好聽佢話 無人會敢反抗 <br />\n球員唔妥教練其實隊隊波都有 問題係唔可以得罪更衣室最有影響力個幾個<br />\n<br />\n摩佬係皇馬本身都只係想整走卡斯 但得罪左西班牙幫 拉膠都借ozil被雪單野公然反抗過 但摩佬都未死得住 但之後佢同阿朗嘈完 得罪埋本身力橕佢既提子派<br />\n最後所有大佬都想佢躝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n車仔就唔駛講啦 剩係夏神同沙皮都夠你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0533c680eab5fbaf0fb6cdbd182329b3a144f39","tid":944402,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0574c094729a06af4d3b386e4a2387e50a850ce2","tid":944402,"uid":33709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"53d830fb7959bddb5603acb2f1f7527f55a7fbf0","tid":944402,"uid":12568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:01:24.000Z","msg":"卡狗收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶頭搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全係更衣室毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"個陣西班牙全靠佢同佩奧爾先勉強團結到喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"返到皇馬帶頭搞事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係老豆駛激到用阿丹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c391e86b3d2ed90eccafc13095a648aea5e33004","tid":944402,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2db18a2753d69e9cb1560d9cf5771ffb085fac33","tid":944402,"uid":36716,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"28589f1e42b83a1feb6004110c349ef7c9f94430","tid":944402,"uid":127870,"like":48,"dislike":9,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"摩佬有幾廢唔judge<br />\n但呢個帶頭係更衣室搞事嘅就收皮啦"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T09:08